ekers|US<br>Heat.]]<br><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/music/pendulum/chart-history/heatseekers-albums|title=Pendulum Chart History: Heatseekers Albums|work=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]|accessdate=16 May 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Hold Your Colour]]''\n|\n* Released: 25 July 2005\n* Label: [[Breakbeat Kaos]] <small>([[Breakbeat Kaos discography|BBK002]])</small>\n* Formats: [[LP album|LP]], [[Compact Disc|CD]], [[Music download|download]]\n| 77 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || 29 || \u2014\n|\n*[[Australian Recording Industry Association|ARIA]]: Gold<ref>[http://www.aria.com.au/pages/httpwww.aria.com.aupagesARIACharts-Accreditations-2009Albums.htm ARIA Charts - Accreditations - 2009 Albums]. [[Australian Recording Industry Association]] (31 December 2009). Retrieved on 9 October 2010.</ref>\n*[[British Phonographic Industry|BPI]]: Platinum<ref name=cert/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[In Silico (Pendulum album)|In Silico]]''\n|\n* Released: 12 May 2008\n* Labels: [[Warner Music Group|Warner Music]], Ear Storm, [[Atlantic Records|Atlantic]] <small>(US)</small>\n* Formats: LP, CD, download\n| 9 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || 21 || \u2014 || 2 || 50\n|\n*BPI: Platinum<ref name=cert/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Immersion (album)|Immersion]]''\n|\n* Released: 24 May 2010\n* Labels: Warner Music, Ear Storm, Atlantic <small>(US)</small>\n* Formats: LP, CD, download\n| 3 || 20 || 67 || 50 || 15 || 48 || 3 || 43 || 1 || 4\n|\n*ARIA: Gold<ref>[http://www.aria.com.au/pages/httpwww.aria.com.aupageshttpwww.aria.com.aupagesARIACharts-Accreditations-2010Albums.htm ARIA Charts - Accreditations - 2010 Albums]. [[Australian Recording Industry Association]] (31 December 2010). Retrieved on 8 April 2011.</ref>\n*BPI: Platinum<ref name=cert/>\n|-\n| colspan=\"13\" style=\"font-size:80%;\"| \"\u2014\" denotes releases that did not chart or were not released in that country.\n|}\n\n===Live albums==