arts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=The+Prodigy&titel=Out+Of+Space+%28Audio+Bullys+Remix%29&cat=s The Prodigy \u2013 \"Out of Space (Audio Bullys remix)\"]. ''norwegiancharts.com''. Retrieved on 17 September 2008. '''Note:''' Released as [[double A-side]], [[Voodoo People / Out of Space|single]] includes referenced song.</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:85%;\"| [[Swiss Hitparade|SWE]]<br><ref>{{cite web|url=https://hitparade.ch/song/The-Prodigy/Voodoo-People-(Pendulum-Remix)-_-Out-Of-Space-157240|title=The Prodigy \u2013 Voodoo People (Pendulum Remix) / Out of Space|website=hitparade.ch|accessdate=15 April 2019}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:85%;\"| [[UK Singles Chart|UK]]<br><ref name=ukcharts/>\n|-\n| 2005\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Voodoo People / Out of Space|Voodoo People]]\"<ref>[[The Prodigy]] (3 October 2005). \"[[Voodoo People / Out of Space]]\". [[XL Recordings]], [http://www.rolldabeats.com/release/xl_recordings/xlt219 ''XLT219''].</ref>\n| [[The Prodigy]]\n| \u2014 || 27 || 20 || 93 || 20\n|''[[Their Law: The Singles 1990\u20132005]]''<ref>[[The Prodigy]] (17 October 2005). ''[[Their Law: The Singles 1990\u20132005]] (Special Edition)''. [[XL Recordings]], [http://www.rolldabeats.com/release/xl_recordings/xlcd190x ''XLCD190X''].</ref>\n|-\n| 2010\n! scope=\"row\"| \"ABC News Theme\"{{ref label|ABC|III|}}\n|Tony Ansell & Peter Wall\n| 38 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n| {{n/a|Non-album single}}\n|-\n| colspan=\"9\" style=\"font-size:80%;\"| \"\u2014\" denotes releases that did not chart or were not released in that country.\n|}\n\n*'''III''' {{Note|ABC}} Released only on Australian [[iTunes Store]].<ref>Peter Wall & Tony Ansell (27 May 2010). \"ABC News Theme\" (remixed by Pendulum). [[iTunes]], [https://itunes.apple.com/au/album/abc-news-theme-remixed-by/id374445947 single]. Retrieved on 25 July 2010.</ref>\n\n==Music videos==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Year !! Song !! Album !! Director !! Type !! Link\n|-\n| 