-who-shot-what-who%E2%80%99s-shooting-what/ PRODUCTION NEWS Who shot what, who\u2019s shooting what\u2026] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120607185029/http://www.promonews.tv/2008/01/15/production-news-who-shot-what-who%E2%80%99s-shooting-what/ |date=7 June 2012 }}. ''Promo News'' (15 January 2008). Retrieved on 10 September 2010.</ref> || Compilation || [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DQA1d0QQvf8]\n|-\n| rowspan=3|2008 || \"Propane Nightmares\" ||  Tim Qualtrough<ref>[http://www.editgods.com/resumes/Tim%20Qualtrough%20Resume.pdf Tim Qualtrough] (PDF). ''editgod.com''. Retrieved on 4 September 2010. {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110710171100/http://www.editgods.com/resumes/Tim%20Qualtrough%20Resume.pdf |date=10 July 2011 }}</ref> || rowspan=3|Narrative || [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WPbeEtjo70g]\n|-\n| \"The Other Side\" ||  Rob Chandler<ref>Knight, David. [http://www.promonews.tv/2008/08/20/pendulum%E2%80%99s-the-other-side-by-rob-chandler/ Pendulum\u2019s \"The Other Side\" by Rob Chandler] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111003035820/http://www.promonews.tv/2008/08/20/pendulum%E2%80%99s-the-other-side-by-rob-chandler/ |date=3 October 2011 }}. ''Promo News'' (20 August 2008). Retrieved on 28 September 2008.</ref> ||[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zENtEumtyBI]\n|-\n| \"Showdown\" || Nick Bartleet<ref>[http://www.promonews.tv/2009/01/15/pendulum%E2%80%99s-showdown-by-nick-bartleet/ Pendulum\u2019s \"Showdown\" by Nick Bartleet] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090121193536/http://www.promonews.tv/2009/01/15/pendulum%E2%80%99s-showdown-by-nick-bartleet/ |date=21 January 2009 }}. ''Promo News'' (15 January 2009). Retrieved on 4 September 2010.</ref> || [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=X6BKBIOtRXw]\n|-\n| rowspan=4|2010 || \"Salt in the Wounds\" || rowspan=5|''Immersion'' || A former Russian army general<ref>[http://www.dogsonacid.com/showthread.php?threadid=671862&mode=article Pendulum's goes 360\u0