7]. [[Twitter]]. Retrieved on 23 December 2010.</ref> || [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8mYd2X_9rrs]\n|}\n\n==Other appearances==\nThe following songs have been made, [[remix]]ed or [[cover version|covered]] by Pendulum, and have not appeared on any studio album or single released by Pendulum.\n\n===Notable compilation appearances===\n{|class=wikitable\n|-\n!Year\n!Song\n!Release\n|-\n|2003\n|\"Vault\"\n|''Kingz of the Rollers EP Volume 3''<ref>Various artists (14 July 2003). (liner notes). 31 Records, [http://www.rolldabeats.com/release/31_records/31r019 ''31R019''].</ref>\n|-\n|rowspan=3|2004\n|\"Toxic Shock\"\n|''The Sideshow EP: Chapter 1''<ref>Various artists (22 March 2004). (liner notes). [[Freak Recordings]], [http://www.rolldabeats.com/release/freak_recordings/freak006 ''FREAK006''].</ref>\n|-\n|\"Kingston Vampires\" <small>(with [[DJ Fresh|Fresh]])</small>\n|rowspan=2|''[[Jungle Sound: The Bassline Strikes Back!]]''<ref name=junglesound/>\n|-\n|\"Masochist\"\n|-\n|2005\n|\"Another Planet\" <small>(VIP mix)</small>\n|''Bass Invaderz''<ref>Various artists (February 2005). ''Bass Invaderz'' (liner notes). [[Human Imprint]], [http://www.rolldabeats.com/release/human_imprint/huma8014_1 ''HUMA8014-1''].</ref>\n|-\n|2006\n|\"Masochist\" <small>(VIP mix)</small>\n|''[[Jungle Sound: Gold]]''<ref name=junglesoundgold/>\n|-\n|2008\n|\"[[Violet Hill (song)|Violet Hill]]\" <small>([[Coldplay]] cover)</small>\n|''[[Radio 1's Live Lounge \u2013 Volume 3]]''<ref>Various artists (20 October 2008). ''[[Radio 1's Live Lounge \u2013 Volume 3]]'' (liner notes). [[Sony Music Entertainment]], [{{Allmusic|class=album|id=r1446005|pure_url=yes}} ''88697391402''].</ref>\n|}\n\n===Guest appearances===\n{|class=wikitable\n|-\n!Year\n!Song\n!Artist\n!Release\n|-\n|2006\n|\"Babylon Rising\"\n|[[DJ Fresh|Fresh]] & Singing Fats\n|''[[Escape from Planet Monday]]''<ref>[[DJ Fresh|Fresh]] (22 May 2006). ''[[Escape from Planet Monday]]'' (liner notes). [[Breakbeat Kaos]], [http://www.rollda