evin |title=Heaven to a Tortured Mind Pitchfork review |url=https://pitchfork.com/reviews/albums/yves-tumor-heaven-to-a-tortured-mind/ |website=Pitchfork |publisher=Pitchfork |accessdate=5 April 2020}}</ref>\n}}\n'''''Heaven to a Tortured Mind''''' is the fourth studio album by [[United States|American]] [[Experimental music|experimental]] [[electronic music|electronic]] artist [[Yves Tumor]], released April 3, 2020.\n\n==Background==\nThe album was announced February 18, 2020 with the release of the single \"Gospel for a New Century\".<ref>{{cite web |last1=Moreland |first1=Quinn |title=Yves Tumor Announces New Album, Shares Video for New Song: Watch |url=https://pitchfork.com/news/yves-tumor-announces-new-album-shares-video-for-new-song-watch/ |website=Pitchfork |publisher=Pitchfork |accessdate=5 April 2020}}</ref> Two more singles followed, \"Kerosene!\" which was released March 9, 2020<ref>{{cite web |last1=Bloom |first1=Madison |title=Listen to Yves Tumor's New Song \"Kerosene\" |url=https://pitchfork.com/news/listen-to-yves-tumor-new-song-kerosene/ |website=Pitchfork |publisher=Pitchfork |accessdate=5 April 2020}}</ref> and \"Romanticist/Dream Palette\", which was released March 31, 2020.<ref>{{cite web |last1=Bloom |first1=Madison |title=Yves Tumor Shares New Song \u201cRomanticist/Dream Palette\u201d: Listen |url=https://pitchfork.com/news/yves-tumor-shares-new-song-romanticistdream-palette-listen/ |website=Pitchfork |publisher=Pitchfork |accessdate=5 April 2020}}</ref>\n\n==Track listing==\nAdapted from LP liner notes.<ref>{{cite web |title=Yves Tumor - Heaven to a Tortured Mind (2020, Silver Vinyl, Vinyl) |url=https://www.discogs.com/Yves-Tumor-Heaven-To-A-Tortured-Mind/release/15040025 |website=Discogs.com |publisher=Discogs |accessdate=5 April 2020}}</ref> {{tracklisting\n|all_writing=[[Yves Tumor]], except where noted\n|extra_column  = Writers\n|title1=Gospel for a New Century\n|title2=Medicine Burn\n|title3=Identity Trade\n|title4=Kerosene!\n|title5=Ha